title: Man Accused of Holding Massive Block Party: 'We Don't Give a F*** About the Coronavirus'
description: An Ohio man accused of violating the state's stay-at-home order said, "We don't give a fuck about the coronavirus," only to be taken away in handcuffs over the weekend.
